Package edu.pdx.cs410J.jsl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Appointment
    The Appointment is the class extended from the AbstractAppointment class that describes an appointment with description, begin time and end time.
    AppointmentBook
    This AppointmentBook class describes who owns a list of appointments and his / her list of appointments.
    AppointmentBookRestClient
    A helper class for accessing the rest client.
    AppointmentBookServlet
    This servlet ultimately provides a REST API for working with an AppointmentBook.
    DateUtility
    A collection of Java Date related utility functions.
    Messages
    Class for formatting messages on the server side.
    PrettyPrinter
    PrettyPrinter is a class that implements AppointmentBookDumper interface.
    Project4
    The main class that parses the command line and communicates with the Appointment Book server using REST.
    TextDumper
    The TextDumper is the class implements the AppointmentBookDumper class.
    TextParser
    The TextParser class implements the AppointmentBookParser.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ParseToken
    This enum is designed to be used in TextDumper and TextParser classes.
